item.title: PLTR
item.description: score:-36 Chances: Palantir has been a popular growth stock for investors bullish on artificial intelligence. The CEO said, ‘We’re all going to get better, faster, smarter’ because of AI. Palantir may see upside from its push into ‘generative’ artificial intelligence. The data mining and analytics company faces a lot of near-term challenges.
